title: You’re Doing Amazing Sweetie: A Kardashian Recap Show | It Was All a Stream
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer and Zack Peter are back to dive into everything Kardashian in episode two! The pair discuss Kylie giving birth (6:00). Then, they get into Kendall’s brain scan (18:00). Later, Amelia and Zack focus in on Travis and Kourtney's PDA as they host Kris and Corey for Dinner in Palm Springs (37:00).
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Zack Peter
Producer: Devon Renaldo
Associate Producer: Jonathan Kermah
